fields.name: AgentName
fields.description: Name of the Agent to assign for new Job Runs of this Job Definition.

fields.name: AgentResourceId
fields.description: Fully qualified resource id of the Agent to assign for new Job Runs of this Job Definition.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: A description for the Job Definition.

fields.name: LatestJobRunName
fields.description: The name of the Job Run in a non-terminal state, if exists.

fields.name: LatestJobRunResourceId
fields.description: The fully qualified resource ID of the Job Run in a non-terminal state, if exists.

fields.name: LatestJobRunStatus
fields.description: The current status of the Job Run in a non-terminal state, if exists.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of this resource.

fields.name: SourceName
fields.description: The name of the source Endpoint.

fields.name: SourceResourceId
fields.description: Fully qualified resource ID of the source Endpoint.

fields.name: SourceSubpath
fields.description: The subpath to use when reading from the source Endpoint.

fields.name: TargetName
fields.description: The name of the target Endpoint.

fields.name: TargetResourceId
fields.description: Fully qualified resource ID of the target Endpoint.

fields.name: TargetSubpath
fields.description: The subpath to use when writing to the target Endpoint.
